    content: `Email marketing delivers an average ROI of £36 for every £1 spent—making it the highest-performing digital marketing channel. Yet most businesses barely scratch the surface of what's possible with email automation.

The difference between average and exceptional email marketing? Automation that delivers the right message to the right person at the right time.

