    content: `46% of all Google searches have local intent. When someone searches "plumber near me" or "best restaurant in Leeds," they're ready to buy. If your business doesn't appear in those results, you're losing customers to competitors who do.

Local SEO is different from traditional SEO. It requires specific strategies to appear in the local pack (the map results) and local organic listings.

Google Business Profile Optimization

