Middle of Funnel (MOFU) - Consideration: Prospects understand their problem and are evaluating solutions. They're comparing options. Content goal: Position your solution and differentiate from competitors.

Bottom of Funnel (BOFU) - Decision: Prospects are ready to buy. They need final reassurance. Content goal: Prove value and reduce risk.

Building Your Automated Funnel

Step 1: Create Lead Magnets

Lead magnets attract prospects and capture their contact information. Effective lead magnets:
- Solve a specific problem
